  "body": "\n\n<div class=\"ohh2-wrap\">\n<div class=\"ohh2-inner\">\n<div class=\"ohh2-chip\">\n<span class=\"ohh2-chip-dot\"></span>\n<span class=\"ohh2-chip-text\">SiteFlow Help Center</span>\n</div>\n<h1 class=\"ohh2-h1\">How can we <em>help</em> you today?</h1>\n<p class=\"ohh2-sub\">Step-by-step guides and answers for every SiteFlow feature — from project setup to payroll.</p>\n<div class=\"ohh2-search-container\">\n<div class=\"ohh2-search-label\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"16.65\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"16.65\"></line></svg>\n        Search all articles\n      </div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-search-pos\">\n<div class=\"ohh2-search-bar\">\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ohh2-search-icon-left\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"16.65\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"16.65\"></line></svg>\n</span>\n<input aria-label=\"Search help articles\" autocomplete=\"off\" class=\"ohh2-search\" id=\"ohh2Input\" placeholder='Search e.g. \"purchase order\", \"attendance\", \"BOQ\"' type=\"text\"/>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ohh2-search-divider\"></span>\n<button aria-label=\"Search\" class=\"ohh2-search-btn\" id=\"ohh2Btn\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"16.65\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"16.65\"></line></svg>\n</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-results-wrap\" id=\"ohh2Results\" role=\"listbox\">\n<div class=\"ohh2-results-hdr\" id=\"ohh2Hdr\"></div>\n<div id=\"ohh2List\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-badges\">\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge\">\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge-icon\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z\"></path><polyline points=\"14 2 14 8 20 8\"></polyline><line x1=\"16\" x2=\"8\" y1=\"13\" y2=\"13\"></line><line x1=\"16\" x2=\"8\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"17\"></line></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge-text\">\n<span class=\"ohh2-badge-title\">Step-by-step guides</span>\n<span class=\"ohh2-badge-sub\">Every feature covered</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge-divider\"></div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge\">\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge-icon\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12 19.79 19.79 0 0 1 1.61 3.39 2 2 0 0 1 3.6 1.22h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l.91-.91a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge-text\">\n<span class=\"ohh2-badge-title\">WhatsApp support</span>\n<span class=\"ohh2-badge-sub\">Dedicated client groups</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge-divider\"></div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge\">\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge-icon\">\n<svg style=\"stroke:#7c3aed\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohh2-badge-text\">\n<span class=\"ohh2-badge-title\">Verified by our team</span>\n<span class=\"ohh2-badge-sub\">Reviewed for every release</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"ohca3-wrap\">\n<div class=\"ohca3-inner\">\n<div class=\"ohca3-label\">\n<span class=\"ohca3-label-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"ohca3-label-text\">Browse by category</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"ohca3-heading\">Find answers for any module</h2>\n<div class=\"ohca3-grid\" id=\"ohca3Grid\">\n<div class=\"ohca3-state\" id=\"ohca3Loading\">Loading categories…</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n ════════════════════════════════════\n     FAQ SECTION\n     FAQPage schema via HTML microdata\n     ════════════════════════════════════ \n<div class=\"ohfq-wrap\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/FAQPage\">\n<div class=\"ohfq-inner\">\n Left: label + heading + support link \n<div class=\"ohfq-left\">\n<div class=\"ohfq-label\">\n<span class=\"ohfq-label-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"ohfq-label-text\">FAQ</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"ohfq-heading\">Common questions about SiteFlow</h2>\n<p class=\"ohfq-sub\">Can’t find what you need? Book a free demo and we will walk you through it live.</p>\n<a class=\"ohfq-support-link\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"16\" rx=\"2\" width=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\"></rect><polyline points=\"3 9 12 15 21 9\"></polyline></svg>\n        Book a Free Demo\n      </a>\n</div>\n Right: accordion \n<div class=\"ohfq-list\" id=\"ohfqList\">\n Q1 \n<div class=\"ohfq-item\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ohfq-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<span class=\"ohfq-q-text\" itemprop=\"name\">How do I log in to SiteFlow?</span>\n<span class=\"ohfq-icon\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"5\" y2=\"19\"></line><line x1=\"5\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohfq-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\">\n<p class=\"ohfq-a-text\" itemprop=\"text\">Open the SiteFlow app or visit <a href=\"https://web.siteflow.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">web.siteflow.com</a>. Enter your registered mobile number and the OTP sent to it. If you do not receive the OTP, tap Resend after 30 seconds or check that your number is registered with your admin. <a href=\"https://siteflow.com/help/getting-started/how-to-log-in-to-SiteFlow/\">Read the full guide →</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n Q2 \n<div class=\"ohfq-item\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ohfq-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<span class=\"ohfq-q-text\" itemprop=\"name\">How do I download the SiteFlow mobile app?</span>\n<span class=\"ohfq-icon\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"5\" y2=\"19\"></line><line x1=\"5\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohfq-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\">\n<p class=\"ohfq-a-text\" itemprop=\"text\">Search for “SiteFlow” on the Google Play Store (Android) or the Apple App Store (iOS). Alternatively, visit <a href=\"https://siteflow.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">siteflow.com</a> and scan the QR code on the homepage. You can also use the web portal at web.siteflow.com without installing anything. <a href=\"https://siteflow.com/help/getting-started/how-to-access-SiteFlow-website-app-and-web-portal/\">Read the full guide →</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n Q3 \n<div class=\"ohfq-item\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ohfq-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<span class=\"ohfq-q-text\" itemprop=\"name\">How do I renew my SiteFlow subscription and add more users?</span>\n<span class=\"ohfq-icon\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"5\" y2=\"19\"></line><line x1=\"5\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohfq-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\">\n<p class=\"ohfq-a-text\" itemprop=\"text\">Renewals and user additions are handled by the SiteFlow team directly. Contact your account manager or reach out with your registered mobile number. You can also request add-ons like Tally integration, Zoho Books, or additional users at the time of renewal. <a href=\"https://siteflow.com/help/getting-started/pricing-and-renewal-in-SiteFlow/\">Read the full guide →</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n Q4 \n<div class=\"ohfq-item\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ohfq-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<span class=\"ohfq-q-text\" itemprop=\"name\">How do I manage multiple GST numbers for different projects?</span>\n<span class=\"ohfq-icon\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"5\" y2=\"19\"></line><line x1=\"5\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohfq-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\">\n<p class=\"ohfq-a-text\" itemprop=\"text\">SiteFlow supports multiple GSTIN numbers under one company account. Go to Company Settings and add each GST number as a separate branch. When creating a project, select the relevant branch so all invoices and transactions for that project use the correct GST.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n Q5 \n<div class=\"ohfq-item\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ohfq-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<span class=\"ohfq-q-text\" itemprop=\"name\">What is the TDS rate for SiteFlow subscription payments?</span>\n<span class=\"ohfq-icon\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"5\" y2=\"19\"></line><line x1=\"5\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohfq-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\">\n<p class=\"ohfq-a-text\" itemprop=\"text\">SiteFlow subscription payments fall under Section 194J of the Income Tax Act (fees for technical services). The applicable TDS rate is 10%. Deduct TDS on the base invoice amount before GST and deposit it to the government. Provide your TDS certificate to the SiteFlow team after deduction.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n Q6 \n<div class=\"ohfq-item\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ohfq-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<span class=\"ohfq-q-text\" itemprop=\"name\">Can I get a refund if I cancel my SiteFlow subscription?</span>\n<span class=\"ohfq-icon\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"5\" y2=\"19\"></line><line x1=\"5\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohfq-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\">\n<p class=\"ohfq-a-text\" itemprop=\"text\">SiteFlow subscriptions are prepaid and non-refundable once activated. If you cancel, your access continues until the end of the current billing period. Auto-renewal can be stopped by contacting the support team before your renewal date. <a href=\"https://siteflow.com/help/getting-started/refund-and-cancellation-policy-SiteFlow/\">Read the full guide →</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n Q7 \n<div class=\"ohfq-item\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ohfq-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<span class=\"ohfq-q-text\" itemprop=\"name\">How do I record expenses that are not linked to any project?</span>\n<span class=\"ohfq-icon\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"5\" y2=\"19\"></line><line x1=\"5\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohfq-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\">\n<p class=\"ohfq-a-text\" itemprop=\"text\">Use the Finance tab at the company level to record overhead and office expenses that are not part of any specific project — such as rent, EMIs, interest payments, or head office expenses. These entries appear in company-level financial reports separately from project costs.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n ════════════════════════════════════\n     ENDING CTA — dark footer scheme\n     Primary CTA → #ct-popup-48098 (Fluent Form popup)\n     Secondary CTA → email support\n     ════════════════════════════════════ \n<div class=\"ohct-wrap\">\n<div class=\"ohct-inner\">\n<div class=\"ohct-eyebrow\">\n<span class=\"ohct-ey-dot\"></span>\n      Still need help?\n    </div>\n<h2 class=\"ohct-h2\">Can’t find what<br/>you’re <em class=\"ohct-h2-em\">looking for?</em></h2>\n<p class=\"ohct-sub\">Book a free demo and we will walk you through any feature live — or reach our support team directly by email.</p>\n<div class=\"ohct-btns\">\n<a class=\"ohct-btn ohct-btn-primary\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"16\" rx=\"2\" width=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\"></rect><polyline points=\"3 9 12 15 21 9\"></polyline></svg>\n        Book a Free Demo\n      </a>\n<a class=\"ohct-btn ohct-btn-outline\" href=\"mailto:support@siteflow.com\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z\"></path><polyline points=\"22,6 12,13 2,6\"></polyline></svg>\n        Email Support\n      </a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ohct-reassurance\">\n<span class=\"ohct-re-item\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg>\n        Free 10-min demo\n      </span>\n<span class=\"ohct-re-item\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg>\n        No credit card needed\n      </span>\n<span class=\"ohct-re-item\">\n<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg>\n        Available in English and Hindi\n      </span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n"
}